SCALE.description: Hi there! SCALE is the base-scale of all size-related tokens (size, space, dimension). The default is 16(px), so it relates to 1rem = 16(px) for font-sizes. If you change it, it will change all size-related tokens.

xxs.description: This is NOT a standard tailwind breakpoint but is important to consider for people using mobile phone web browsers.

intensity-01.description: Drop shadows are more visible on light backgrounds than dark ones. In order to be able to intensify the drop shadows on dark theme, you can use a variable/token like this and bump it up in your dark theme.
